## No Emojis in Code

@rule {
    "id": "no-emojis",
    "severity": "error",
    "rationale": "Emojis in code reduce readability, cause encoding issues, and are unprofessional"
}

Never use emojis in:
- Variable names
- Function names
- Class names
- Comments
- String literals
- Any part of the code file

